                            Conditional Statements
        
        -- When we want to run some code based on certain condition otherwise wants to skip the 
          execution of that code.

      
    1) if:

      Syntax:
        if(condition){
          // when the condition is true
        }

    2) if-else:

        Syntax:
          if(condition){
            // when the condition is true
          }
          else{
            // when the condition is false
          }

    3) else-if ladder:
        Syntax:
          if(condition1){
            // when the condition1 is true
          }
          else if(condition2){
            // when the condition2 is true
          }
          else if(condition3){
            // when the condition3 is true
          }
          else{
            // When all the conditions are false
          }
    
    4) Nested if-else:

      Syntax: 
        if(condition){
          if(condition2){

          }else{

          }
        }else{

        }

    5) Switch-case:
        
        // condition should generally be a variable which is whole number.
        switch(condition){
          case :

          break;

          case: 
          
          break;
        }